<h1>Tracking Issues</h1>

<h3>These are issues that if they cross thresholds we should alert in some manor</h3>

* Server / Database Monitoring

   * Server ping >= 100ms or total failure
   
   * DB connection time >= 100ms or total failure
   
   * MountPoint UsedPct >= 80% & >=95%
   
   * CPU load >= 3xCpuCount & >= 10xCpuCount
   
   * CPU Idle Pct <= 10%
   
   * Cluster Health: Active Host < Hosts  & Active Host <= 1
